data.description: Ranging pricing 375,000 - 400,000 Discover a 4-bed, 2.5-bath gem in Rita Ranch. This unique home features a 3-car garage and a flex space. Flex space thoughtfully added to of the garage spaces, complete with a built-in air-conditioned room. This versatile bonus room can be used as a home office, gym, art studio, or even a playroom - the possibilities are endless! Step outside to the beautifully landscaped backyard, where you'll find a covered patio and ample room for outdoor activities. This outdoor space is perfect for enjoying the Arizona sun, hosting barbecues, or simply unwinding after a long day. The Vail school district, Rita Ranch, Boosts excellent schools, beautiful parks, and convenient access to shopping, dining, and entertainment. With the added advantage of a 3-car garage
